Package task

Class Statistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • task.Statistics
  • public class Statistics
extends java.lang.Object
    The `Statistics` class represents task statistics, including the number of tasks completed within the last week, the total number of tasks completed, the percentage of tasks completed within the last week, and the percentage of total tasks completed.
    Version:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    raydenlim
